query:
INSERT INTO places (atollId, name, code, type)
SELECT 
  a.id,
  ig.name,
  LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(ig.slug, '-', '_'), ' ', '_'), '--', '_')),
  'island'
FROM (
  SELECT 
    name,
    slug,
    atoll,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY name, atoll ORDER BY id) as rn
  FROM island_guides
  WHERE contentType = 'island'
) ig
LEFT JOIN atolls a ON ig.atoll = a.name
WHERE ig.rn = 1
